body: "Client: events queued at ~/.pm-cli/runtime/telemetry/events.jsonl with attempt tracking and exponential backoff. pm health --check-telemetry probes healthz endpoint. PM_TELEMETRY_DISABLED=1 disables telemetry. Redaction works for recent max capture level events. Server: all [redacted_service_count] services up and healthy. [redacted_queue_service] has 0 pending messages with 1 active consumer. [redacted_datastore] has events from 2026-04-25 to present. Dogfood events visible with source_context=dogfood in [redacted_datastore]. [redacted_monitoring_ui] at [redacted_monitoring_host] accessible. No secrets in repo (check-secrets.mjs passes)."
